<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Animal biology bridges the gap between general biological sciences and applied animal husbandry techniques. As an Animal Biology major, you put your theoretical knowledge into practice by working with wild and domesticated animals in hands-on situations.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
